{
  "stem": "13063.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory-- the shirts that my father manufactured were known under the name of [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means, special shirts--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in French.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, only my mother [INAUDIBLE] helped out in the business, and she was there almost daily, to oversee the work and to-- also to be a part of a very growing and thriving business.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really thriving, because my father started very small-- on a very small scale-- and it developed into a very serious-- very serious manufacturing business.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was home, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he traveled a lot, because to sell shirts, you see, to make contact with-- with clienteleship, with clientele, she had-- he had to travel in Poland-- mostly in Poland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most of the time, he went in the morning, and he was back at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father, who was a traditional man, he had a very fine and pleasant voice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he'd really like to be a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He very-- he was really tickled when-- when asked to daven a [HEBREW] Shabbat or on a Shabbat when he was in shul.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Usually, we went-- my father liked a small shul where there was a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, the rabbi was connected with the [HEBREW]-- with the [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- he liked to-- a small-- a small surrounding, a small room where they davened, I would say-- unofficially.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was born in Cracow on Dietla Street, D-I-E-T-L-A-- Dietla Street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, we moved on Dietla Street three times-- or, really, twice-- from 29-- number 29, where I was born-- to 57.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a few years, and then 63 where the war-- when the war came and found us, right there at Dietla 63.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
